these historical relations,

00:54:09.910 --> 00:54:12.550
and the extent to
which we may be living

00:54:12.550 --> 00:54:15.400
through certain
forms of rupture,

00:54:15.400 --> 00:54:18.850
and whether there's
some question about what

00:54:18.850 --> 00:54:25.550
language is required to map
these historical relations.

00:54:25.550 --> 00:54:28.338
John, you can answer
about my book.

00:54:28.338 --> 00:54:31.150
