00:56:00.580 --> 00:56:02.740
So I've written about boredom.

00:56:02.740 --> 00:56:04.150
I've written about idleness.

00:56:04.150 --> 00:56:07.120
I've written about laziness.

00:56:07.120 --> 00:56:11.590
And I thought maybe my
impairment has enabled me.

00:56:11.590 --> 00:56:15.610
I see people looking
aghast in the audience.

00:56:15.610 --> 00:56:17.910
The X-ray was wrong.

00:56:17.910 --> 00:56:20.290
[LAUGHTER]

00:56:20.290 --> 00:56:24.430
Basically there was a
whole part of the X-ray

00:56:24.430 --> 00:56:26.270
