01:21:20.990 --> 01:21:24.740
into, I don't know whether
to call it affect, or drives,

01:21:24.740 --> 01:21:28.240
or do you see what I'm saying?

01:21:28.240 --> 01:21:30.940
The opening of the windows.

01:21:30.940 --> 01:21:32.650
Getting out of the monad.

01:21:32.650 --> 01:21:35.800
Yeah, just.

01:21:35.800 --> 01:21:37.580
I guess.

01:21:37.580 --> 01:21:38.650
I don't know.

01:21:38.650 --> 01:21:41.470
What do you think?

01:21:41.470 --> 01:21:45.220
Well, can I circle
